<br>
But I noticed a few Bard issues that I would like to point out.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
1. Chant of Battle. Currently listed as an &quot;ability&quot; in the level field. It should just say the level (1).<br>
<br>
2. Amplification. The song description reads funny: &quot;Increase Singing Amplification for between -95% (L30) to -91% (L60) in 5 ticks&quot;. Try to word it without the negatives, if possible.<br>
<br>
3. Melody of Ervaj. Descriptions says &quot;Increase Mana Drain by 105 (L50)&quot; whereas it should read &quot;Increase Haste by 5%&quot;. Something about it stacking with all other Haste (including Vah Shir) but not exceeding the Cap would be nice, as well.<br>
<br>
4. Battlecry of the Vah Shir. Please add in something about it stacking with all other forms of Haste.<br>
<br>
5. Occlusion of Sound. In the details it mentions &quot;Song requires a 13000&quot;, this should read &quot;Song requires a Drum&quot;.<br>
<br>
6. Composition of Ervaj. Same deal as #3, only this one is 10% Haste.<br>
<br>
7. Warsong of the Vah Shir. Same as #4.<br>
<br>
-------------<br>
<br>
PS, sorry to nitpick!  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
