<br>
1) I looks like you're taking all the spells in the file that are level one and take 0 mana, and marking them as an Ability.  This should work just fine, except for bards.  Changing this check to &quot;all spells that are level one, take no mana, and class != bard&quot; would make it work correctly (or some similar change, I would bet).<br>
<br>
2) The &quot;Singing Amplification&quot; attribute has changed format since luclin came out.  EQcaster had previously been interpreting it correctly, but now its kinda funky.  I would recomending changing it to read:<br>
<br>
&quot;Increases singing modifier for between 0.5 (L30) to 0.9 (L60) in 5 ticks.&quot;<br>
<br>
0.5 and 0.9 are just (2+30/8)/10 and (2+60/8)/10 (rounded to one decimal place).  This change would make it acurately discribe how the song effects bards.<br>
<br>
3) Currently the &quot;Song requires a *something*&quot; field isn't exactly correct.  All songs that require an instrument have an entry in the &quot;Reagent 1&quot; collumn, but some songs that do not require one also have an entry in this collumn.  The correct collumn for this would be &quot;Focus 1&quot;.<br>
<br>
I'm not certain what the &quot;Reagent 1&quot; collumn is supposed to be.  Some songs that can use an instrument have an entry here, but others do not.<br>
<br>
Plus, as Keiz said above, a 13000 is a drum.<br>
<br>
Heres to hoping that this is helpful. <p>-<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=4773">Ruldar Swiftnote</a> [Swords for Hire]<BR>58 Troubadour of the Rathe</p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=13160.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=13160.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=13160.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a> <b>4</b> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=13160.topic&start=81&stop=81>5</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=13160.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=13160.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13160.topic&index=66><img src=http://www.graffe.com/messageboard/add_reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=13160.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.threadControl?topicID=13160.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=13160.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies